==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[fee]] [[schedule]]}}

# A list or table, whether ordered or not, showing fixed fees for goods or services.
# The actual set of fees to be charged.
===Adjective===

# Listed on, or belonging to, a fee schedule (n.).

